Sphere: Mind Sphere<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage summer rain<br/><br/>
<br/>
Casting summer rain will summon a healing rain from a cloudy sky that will<br/>
provide healing to all who are in the room.  The spell will only work if it<br/>
is either cloudy or raining.<br/>
